<section class="intro-section">
    <div class="overlay">
        <h1>Make awesome mod lists faster and easier.</h1>
        <h2>Mod Picker helps you find compatible mods to personalize your gaming experience.</h2>

        <a class="btn big-btn" href="users/sign_up">Get Started</a>

